  "content": {
    "tiles": [
      {
        "id": "eHHFbsMV_ZP0h-rW",
        "title": "Text 1",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>The students so a few trials to find their walking backward rate.</p><ul><li>Wilson walks backward at 1/4 miles in 5 minutes.</li><li>Sam walks backward at 1/5 miles in 4 minutes.</li></ul><ul><ul><li>Who has the greater walking rate? Explain</li></ul></ul>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "WRf1gKt6eAHJqkWz",
        "title": "Text 2",
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>They have the same walking rate.</p><p>Some students might find an equivalent rate in terms of distance.</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      [
        {
          "id": "YCA6hElx9OMDhP_G",
          "title": "Text 3",
          "display": "teacher",
          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<p>Wilson → 1/4 mile in 5 minutes</p><p>                         ↓ × 4            ↓ × 4</p><p>                         1 mile in 20 minutes</p>"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "ARl1Iqaebp0Nr9W0",
          "title": "Text 4",
          "display": "teacher",
          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<p>Sam → 1/5 miles in 4 minutes</p><p>                     ↓ × 5            ↓ × 5</p><p>                    1 miles in 20 minutes</p>"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      {
        "id": "swRNo7KwyZrqG1Uk",
        "title": "Text 5",
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>Some students might find an equivalent rate in terms of time</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      [
        {
          "id": "GldxDX249cMHmyln",
          "title": "Text 6",
          "display": "teacher",
          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<p>Wilson → 1/4 mile in 5 minutes</p><p>                         ↓ ÷ 5            ↓ ÷ 5</p><p>                      1/20 mile in 1 minute</p>"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "F8-w24FPghIuhx4q",
          "title": "Text 7",
          "display": "teacher",
          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<p>Sam → 1/5 mile in 4 minutes</p><p>                  ↓ ÷ 4            ↓ ÷ 4</p><p>                1/20 mile in 1 minute</p>"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    ]
  },
